     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     SETOF                     10
     C                     Z-ADD0         WSURY   30
     C                     READ AFAWP33                  10
     C           *IN10     IFEQ '0'
      *
     C*----------------------------*
     C*  ..箱数＝Ｃ箱比率計算..  *
