     C           WSG1      DIV  CBBARL    WSG2    40
     C           CBBARL    MULT WSG2      WSG21   40
     C           WSG21     MULT WCBKO     WSGK    40
     C           CBHK,D    SUB  WSGK      WSG3    40
     C                     ADD  WSG21     WMAIS
     C                     ADD  WSGK      WSURY
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWSG21     $MAIS
