      *
     C                     MOVE CBSHN1    @SHN1
     C                     MOVE CBSHN2    @SHN2
     C                     MOVE CBSHN3    @SHN3
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    @DTKB
     C                     Z-ADD0         @HTYY
     C                     Z-ADD0         @HTMM
     C                     Z-ADD0         @HTDD
     C                     Z-ADD0         @HTBB
     C                     EXSR SBMSK
      *
